  (map (lambda (k)
         (let ((n (* k divisor)))
           (display (string-append 
                      (number->string n) \" ÷ \" 
                      (number->string divisor) \" = \" 
                      (number->string k)))
           (newline)
           k))
       (range 1 (+ limit 1))))

(division-table 5 10)
```

[VISUAL: A printed table:
