### Example 3.23: Zero Divided by Anything (Always 0)

What about zero divided by something?

<!-- BUILD: Prints 0 ÷ n for n from 1 to 10. -->

```scheme
(map (lambda (n)
       (display (string-append 
                  \"0 ÷ \" (number->string n) \" = \" 
                  (number->string (quotient 0 n))))
       (newline)
       (quotient 0 n))
     (range 1 11))
```

[VISUAL: A printed table:
